title: "Hey, DT! Please Make a Non-Linux YouTube Channel." (Plus Other Comments!)
description:
On this edition of HEY DT:

0:00 Intro
0:20 Hey, DT! I couldn't get DTOS to install.
4:39 Hey DT, I would be interested in you setting up a basic Xorg environment. TWM + Xterm...
6:30 Hey DT, how's the Moonlander keyboard? 
9:48 Hey DT, just saw this old video of yours and it reminded me...I have an 84 key keyboard.
11:39 Hey DT... My wife says she really likes your voice lol. 😅❤
11:49 Hey DT, Thank you, this is one of your best videos...U don't have to answer but do you play hockey?
12:50 Hey DT I’m shocked you’re not using straight.el for Emacs package management.
13:55 Hey DT, thank you for teaching CLI functions! ... I get deleted alot. :D
16:24 Hey DT, why not make a separate channel to discuss non-Linux topics? I'd follow it.
19:19 Thanks to the Patrons!
